                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "There you are. Unaccounted foot traffic on a load-bearing stairwell. That is a line item, and line items get billed. Luckily for you, this branch is running a promotion."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The Customer Confidence Challenge. You stake 150 CobbleDollars on yourself. Win, and the branch doubles it back with training supplies. Lose, and your stake becomes a rounding error I am very fond of."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Analyst — unaccounted foot traffic",
                    Label: "approach_billed"
