                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Terms. The stake is 150, collected up front, held by the branch. A win returns 300 plus two great balls, which the ledger books as a customer confidence event. A loss returns a receipt. The receipt is commemorative."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The model says nobody takes the challenge twice. The model is very proud of that number."
                        }
                    ],
